text.tspan: I wanted my username to be Joo_Maria_Jos_Francisco_Xavier_de_Paula_Luis_Antonio_
Domingos_Rafael_de_Bragana, but it was already taken. :( You can just call me Your Majesty.
Your Majesty is married to a spicy Spanish churro with a bad
leg but a truly covetable mustache. On the wedding night,
Carlota Joaquina threw a candlestick at the royal cabea and
nearly bit the regal ear off. We're separated now, ladies (or
Recently the royal family relocated from Portugal to Brazil. The French and the
English were squabbling over Portugal and Your Macho Manjesty felt the need
to clear his head for a bit. Preferably while it was still attached to his shoulders.
